聆听 Little Simz 与 Sampha 联手深情的“卫星商业 2.0” https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-sampha-soulful-satellite-business-2-0-3776230?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=little-simz-sampha-soulful-satellite-business- 2-0Daniel Peters Fri, 19 Jul 2024 04:20:15 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicRapUK rap https://www.nme.com/?p=3776230 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="桑帕·利特尔·西姆兹" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> “一段时间以来，Simz 的音乐一直贴近我的心和耳朵”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-sampha-soulful-satellite-business-2-0-3776230">《聆听 Little Simz 与 Sampha 联手打造深情的“卫星商业 2.0”》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="桑帕·利特尔·西姆兹" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">Sampha</a>发行了“Satellite Business 2.0”，这是他的“Lahai”曲目的扩展版本，现在由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a>主演。听下面的曲目。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/little-simz-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-stage-setlist-photos-3770489">Little Simz 在 Glastonbury 2024：一位历史上伟大的英国说唱歌手登上了头条新闻的地位</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首新单曲是 Sampha 2023 年第二张专辑中插曲《Satellite Business》的扩展。 “《Satellite Business》是《Lahai》最后录制的曲目之一，我一直想用一首客串诗来扩展它，”他在<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/sampha-and-little-simz-link-up-on-satellite-business-2-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《The Line of Best Fit》</em></a>的一份新闻声明中说道。</p><p> “一段时间以来，Simz 的音乐一直贴近我的心和耳朵，这让她在这首歌中的表现更加特别。她是我最喜欢的艺术家之一。她的自信和创造性的勇气令人耳目一新，看到有人为自己的艺术付出如此多的努力真是令人惊叹”。</p><p>与此同时，Little Simz 表示，她“非常荣幸能与 Sampha 一起制作这张唱片”，并称他“确实是当今音乐界最重要的声音之一”。她补充道：“我们有很好的音乐化学反应，并且尊重彼此的过程。很高兴我能在这件事上与他站在一起。” </p><p><iframe title="Sampha 和 Little Simz - 卫星业务 2.0" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/THre1r5KGR0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Sampha 在 Instagram 帖子中详细阐述了“Satellite Business 2.0”的起源，称这首原创歌曲“是在去年的现场演奏中演变而来的”，观众的反响激励他继续创作这首新歌曲。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9fhlfLNK1r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-rig